is_symm_from_blocks_iff:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.transpose -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.transpose -/
/-- This is the `iff` version of `matrix.is_symm.from_blocks`. -/
theorem is_symm_from_blocks_iff {A : matrix m m α} {B : matrix m n α} {C : matrix n m α} {D : matrix n n α} :
    (A.from_blocks B C D).is_symm ↔ A.is_symm ∧ matrix.transpose B = C ∧ matrix.transpose C = B ∧ D.is_symm :=
  ⟨fun h => ⟨congr_arg to_blocks₁₁ h, congr_arg to_blocks₂₁ h, congr_arg to_blocks₁₂ h, congr_arg to_blocks₂₂ h⟩,
    fun ⟨hA, hBC, hCB, hD⟩ => is_symm.from_blocks hA hBC hD⟩
#align is_symm_from_blocks_iff is_symm_from_blocks_iff

from_blocks:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.transpose -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.transpose -/
/-- A block matrix `A.from_blocks B C D` is symmetric,
    if `A` and `D` are symmetric and `Bᵀ = C`. -/
theorem is_symm.from_blocks {A : matrix m m α} {B : matrix m n α} {C : matrix n m α} {D : matrix n n α} (hA : A.is_symm)
    (hBC : matrix.transpose B = C) (hD : D.is_symm) : (A.from_blocks B C D).is_symm :=
  by
  have hCB : matrix.transpose C = B := by
    rw [← hBC]
    simp
  unfold matrix.is_symm
  rw [from_blocks_transpose]
  congr <;> assumption
#align is_symm.from_blocks is_symm.from_blocks
